<style>.commentItem { display: none; border: 1px solid #b0b0b0; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }</style><p><b>Visitor Submitted Comments</b></p><p id='showAllCommand' style='display: none;'><a href='javascript:showAllComments();'>Show older comments</a></p><div id='commentItem1' class='commentItem' style='background-color: #f0f0f0'>1. <span style='font-style: italic;'>william Sarratt</span> says:<br /><small>12 Apr 2010 05:27:49 AM</small><br /><br />Can anyone shed some light as to what may have happened or did they know seamen Algie Reed.He is my wife's uncle and she is trying to find out and pay honor to him and the crew of the Saint Louis.We have very little info if any.I also think she is trying to help her dad find out whom himself is getting later in life.Please help if you can.

